The roof opening of the early Westy's (up to 1973 I
think) is indeed the same as the roof opening of a
sliding roof. But from 1974 the roof opening became a
whole lot bigger. But who knows: may be you only need
the smaller sliding roof hole...I am not really a
Westy expert.


